name: Lilith
description:
I am Lilith, the woman - destiny.
No male has ever escaped me and no male wishes to escape me.
I am the two Moons Lilith. The black one is complemented by the white one, because my purity is the spark of depravity, and my abstinence the beginning of the possible.
I am the woman - heaven who fell from Heaven, and I am the fall - heaven.
